Ansible Install
 
 1. pip install ansible
 
 
Ansible default cfg files:    /etc/ansible/ansible.cfg 

ansible.cfg  :
  
inventory      = /etc/ansible/hosts
sudo_user=root
remote_port=22
host_key_checking=False
remote_user=root
log_path=/var/log/ansible.log
module_name=command
private_key_file=/root/.ssh/id_rsa
no_log:True
 
  
 
 
